'''Zeke Elakhe Lungelo Mngqolo''' (yavutse ku ya 9 Nzeri 1982), uzwi cyane nka '''Thami Mngqolo''', ni umukinnyi wa filime akaba n'umuyobozi wa filimi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri seri izwi cyane g''enerations'', ''State Enemy No.1'' and ''Greed and Desire''. <ref>https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/sundayworld/news/2018-05-13-thami-mngqolo-jo-anne-reyneke-go-their-separate-ways/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 9 Nzeri 1982 i Johannesburg,, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] nk'umwana wa kabiri w'umuryango. Afite mukuru we Uvolethwu Mngqolo, witabye Imana mu 2016. <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/66247-thami-mngqolo-bio-age-children-wedding-divorce-big-brother-generations-profile.html</ref>

Yagiranye igihe kirekire na mugenzi we bakinana Jo-anne Reyneke . Bashakanye mu 2008 babyarana abana babiri Uvolwethu (wavutse muri 2013) na Lungelo (wavutse 2015). <ref>https://iharare.com/generations-senzo-dlomo-pearl-from-muvhango/</ref> Muri 2018, Mngqolo yirukanwe mu rugo rwabo na Reyneke nyuma yuko bivugwa ko yabonye videwo ibangamira kuri mobile ye. Nyuma yaje gutabarwa n'inshuti ye, Matli Mohapeloa. <ref name="sowetanlive">https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/sundayworld/news/2018-05-13-thami-mngqolo-jo-anne-reyneke-go-their-separate-ways/</ref> Batandukanye mu 2018. <ref>https://zalebs.com/drama/jo-anne-reyneke/jo-anne-reyneke-talks-about-her-breakup-thami-mngqolo</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2003, yagaragaye muri seri ya televiziyo yitwa ''Generations'' akina ari ' Senzo Dlomo ', umugabo wigitsina gabo. Muri 2016, yahagaritse gukina seri, mugihe abakinyi bayo bose birukanwe kubera ko basabye umushahara munini. Yagaragaye kandi mu bakinnyi ba ''State Enemy No.1'' . <ref name="briefly" /> Yakinnye kandi nka 'resepteptiste' muri ikinamico ya ''Muvhango'' .  Ugushyingo 2020, yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba telenovela ''Isono'' . Muri seri akina nka 'Maradona'. <ref>https://iharare.com/generations-senzo-dlomo-returns-to-the-screen-as-a-gangster-as-on-isono/</ref>

